Package: equalityml
Type: Package
Title: Algorithms for Assessing Fairness and Mitigating Bias in Supervised Machine Learning
Description: EqualityML provides tools and guidance on how to include fairness and bias 
   mitigation methods to model fitting so as to safeguard the people on the receiving 
   end of our models from bias.
Version: 0.1.0.9000
